				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 about-left">
					<figure class="effect-bubba">
						<img class="img-responsive" src="/Content/images/abt-2.jpg" alt=""/>
						<figcaption>
							<h4>Maximum luxury</h4>
							<p> You will be able to attract everyone's attention thanks to luxury. </p>	
						</figcaption>			
					</figure>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 about-left">
					<figure class="effect-bubba">
